import { Text, View } from "react-native"


const RepositoryItemStats = ({ stars, forks, reviews, rating }) => {
  return (
    <View>
      <View>
        <Text>{stars}</Text>
        <Text>Stars</Text>
      </View>
      <View>
        <Text>{forks}</Text>
        <Text>Forks</Text>
      </View>
      <View>
        <Text>{reviews}</Text>
        <Text>Reviews</Text>
      </View>
      <View>
        <Text></Text>
        <Text>Rating</Text>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
};

export default RepositoryItemStats;
